[25/09/2018 20:54:37] <font color="#ffffff">(Música)</font>
[25/09/2018 20:54:39] <font color="#ffffff">"Ir caminando</font>
[25/09/2018 20:54:39] <font color="#ffffff">del East al West Village</font>
